Either the native update query or JPQL update query just return `int` which is no of records updated and also they need `@Modifying` annotation [Update Queries][1]

**JPQL**

    @Modifying
    @Query(&quot;update User u set u.status = :status where u.name = :name&quot;)
    int updateUserSetStatusForName(@Param(&quot;status&quot;) Integer status, 
      @Param(&quot;name&quot;) String name);

